==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Pee
<hw>Pee</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Naut.)</fld> <def>Bill of
an anchor. See <er>Peak</er>, 3 <sd>(c)</sd>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Urine.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>The act of urinating; -- used in the informal
<col>take a pee</col>, meaning, to urinate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>pee</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
